frames.caption: A person relaxes on a bed with a view of the illuminated pyramids under a starry night sky. The scene is framed by ancient Egyptian columns and curtains, creating a sense of historical grandeur. Palm trees and a cityscape are visible in the distance, enhancing the exotic atmosphere.
